h%20Naina%20was%20the%20one%20with%20the%20diagnosis%2C%20schizophrenia%20consumed%20the%20entire%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20rocky%20road%20to%20a%20diagnosis%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20Naina%20would%20claim%20to%20hear%20and%20see%20things%20and%20would%20isolate%20herself%20at%20times.%20But%20things%20took%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse%20after%20two%20stressful%20events%20in%20her%20personal%20life%20pushed%20her%20to%20the%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shaji%20S%2C%20Chief%20Psychiatrist%20at%20Bethesda%20Hospital%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20schizophrenia%2C%20trauma%20is%20the%20trigger%20to%20the%20pre-existing%20vulnerability.%20The%20biological%20makeup%20of%20the%20mind%20and%20its%20genetic%20vulnerability%20is%20as%20important%20as%20the%20environmental%20factors%2C%20childhood%20experiences%20and%20parental%20styles%20that%20affect%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20development.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20local%20mental%20health%20institutions%20grossly%20understaffed%20and%20under-resourced%2C%20the%20family%20struggled%20to%20get%20help.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20facilities%20in%20our%20small%20town%20were%20like%20what%20you%20see%20in%20old%20films%20%E2%80%94%20neglected%20and%20grim%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mahira%20recalls.%20Eventually%2C%20they%20found%20the%20right%20support%20at%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Mental%20Health%20and%20Neuro%20Sciences%20(NIMHANS)%2C%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-52_11zon-1748415777.jp