er%20the%20last%20year%2C%20with%20Russia%20often%20sending%20hundreds%20at%20a%20target%20in%20one%20night%20to%20overwhelm%20Ukrainian%20air%20defenses.%20They're%20combined%20with%20waves%20of%20long-range%20missile%20strikes%2C%20making%20the%20night%20attacks%20even%20deadlier%20and%20more%20difficult%20to%20mitigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20launched%20Shaheds%20are%20cheaper%20versions%20without%20warheads%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-found-western-parts-russian-decoy-drone-fools-air-defenses-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eserve%20as%20decoys%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Ihnat%20estimated%20to%20RBC%20Ukraine%20that%20for%20every%20100%20drones%20sent%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20about%2040%20are%20usually%20decoys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShaheds%20are%20slower%20and%20typically%20less%20powerful%20than%20cruise%20or%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20but%20they%20cost%20less%2C%20at%20about%20%2420%2C000%20to%20%2450%2C000%20per%20drone.%20Even%20lower-end%20air%20defense%20missiles%2C%20like%20the%20medium-range%20interceptor%20fired%20from%20the%20Soviet%20Buk-M1%2C%20can%20cost%20about%20%24300%2C000%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US-made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-patriot-missile-defense-system-cost-middle-east-syria-iraq-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPatriot%20missile%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20of%20which%20Ukraine%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20about%20six%20to%20eight%2C%20fires%20interceptors%20that%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpatriot-missile-makers-get-zelenskyy-praise-ukraine-amid-shortage-concerns-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecost%20up%20to%20%244%20million%20each.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20cost%20disparity%20has%20fueled%20Moscow's%20push%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-making-own-versions-iranian-attack-drones-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuild%20Shaheds%20locally%3C%2F