0USB-A%20ports%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECar%20socket%20outlet%20(like%20the%20car%20cigarette%20lighter%20of%20yesteryear)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20particular%20note%20is%20that%20you%20don't%20need%20an%20additional%20240-volt%20adapter%20to%20use%20heavy%20appliances%2C%20like%20ovens%2C%20EV%20charging%2C%20or%20dryers.%20You%20can%20plug%20them%20directly%20into%20the%20appropriate%20outlets%20on%20the%20unit.%20This%20versatility%20makes%20the%20Anker%20Solix%20F3800%20an%20effective%20option%20for%20garage%20workshops%2C%20emergency%20home%20backup%2C%20outdoor%20events%2C%20and%20RV%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22144394e4-d431-41e8-bc3d-e46335d78e99%5C%22%3ECapacity%20and%20performance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221599%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Several%20items%2C%20including%20a%20humidifier%2C%20laptop%2C%20and%20more%2C%20are%20plugged%20into%20the%20Anker%20Solix%20F3800%20power%20station.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6785592350dfd88e193e1a73%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221199%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20fan%2C%20humidifier%2C%20electric%20kettle%2C%20and%20charging%20laptop%20didn't%20come%20close%20to%20overloading%20the%20Anker%20Solix%20F3800%2C%20which%20can%20handle%20up%20to%206%2C000W%20at%20a%20time.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Anker%20Solix%20F3800's%20base%20capacity%20is%20impressive%20at%203%2C840%20watt-hours%20(Wh)%2C%20which%20basically%20means%20you%20could%20run%20a%203%2C840W%20appliance%20for%20an%20hour%20with%20it.%20Fortunately%2C%20most%20appliances%20are%20well%20under%20that%20size%2C%20so%20you%20can%20run%20them%20for%20several%20hours.%20We'll%20get%20into%20examples%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20purchase%20expansion%20batteries%20from%20Anker%20for%20up%20to%2053%2C800Wh%2C%20so%20you%20can%20slowly%20build%20up%20your%20home's%20power%20backup%20over%20time.%20With%20the