-Portable-Generator-Expandable%252Fdp%252FB0CFVBGWBT%253Fth%253D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJackery%20Explorer%201000%20Plus%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20the%20same%20test%2C%20and%20its%20usable%20capacity%20was%20slightly%20less%20(82%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20I%20plugged%20in%20multiple%20power-hungry%20appliances%20%E2%80%94%20like%20trying%20to%20run%20a%20toaster%2C%20coffee%20maker%2C%20refrigerator%2C%20and%20microwave%20simultaneously.%20Only%2C%20I%20used%20even%20higher-wattage%20appliances%3A%20space%20heaters%20and%20air%20fryers%20ranging%20from%201%2C500W%20to%201%2C700W%20each.%20I%20could%20run%20two%20space%20heaters%20and%20an%20air%20fryer%2C%20about%204%2C700W%2C%20without%20any%20problem.%20But%2C%20it's%20like%20filling%20a%20bucket%20%E2%80%94%20the%20power%20station%20can%20handle%206%2C000W%20total%20(the%20size%20of%20the%20bucket).%20So%2C%20when%20we%20added%20the%20fourth%20appliance%2C%20it%20overfilled%20the%206%2C000W%20capacity.%20Instead%20of%20breaking%2C%20it%20turned%20itself%20off%20and%20gave%20an%20%26quot%3Boverload%26quot%3B%20warning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b679c3bb-5c90-49c4-9a6d-f182b4de9559%5C%22%3ECharging%20capabilities%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221599%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20closeup%20of%20the%20Anker%20Solix%20F3800%20portable%20power%20station's%20display.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678574028951662c9f1fe992%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221199%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20on-unit%20display%20show%20you%20how%20much%20charge%20is%20left%20and%20approximately%20how%20long%20it%20will%20last%20based%20on%20current%20usage.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Anker%20Solix%20power%20station%20has%20various%20charging%20methods.%20The%20easiest%20is%20just%20plugging%20it%20into%20your%20wall%20outlet.%20You%20can%20adjust%20how%20quickly%20it%20charges%20in%20the