5%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-39_11zon-1748265016-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-39_11zon-1748265016-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-39_11zon-1748265016-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-39_11zon-1748265016-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-439246%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJamawar%20shawls%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20worn%20%E2%80%94%20they%E2%80%99re%20inherited.%20Each%20thread%20tells%20a%20story%20of%20Kashmiri%20heritage%20and%20timeless%20craft.%20Picture%20source%3A%20Shahkaar%20(L)%20and%20The%20House%20of%20Naqash%20(R)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20to%20ensure%20its%20longevity%2C%20he%20is%20breathing%20new%20life%20into%20a%20forgotten%20art%20form%20and%20is%20actively%20working%20to%20pass%20it%20down%20to%20the%20next%20generation%2C%20envisioning%20a%20legacy%20that%20will%20thrive%20for%20centuries%20to%20come.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20take%20this%20art%20forward%2C%20but%20the%20government%20should%20establish%20a%20dedicated%20training%20centre%20where%20aspiring%20artisans%20and%20young%20students%20can%20learn%20the%20craft%20with%20ease.%20The%20work%20is%20demanding%2C%20and%20a%20single%20shawl%20can%20take%20months%20or%20even%20years%20to%20complete.%20It%20takes%20three%20months%20to%20start%20work%20on%20a%20shawl%20from%20scratch%20until%20completion.%20The%20work%20demands%20a%20lot%20of%20patience%2C%20which%20is%20why%20people%20are%20fleeing%20from%20this%20art%20and%20refusing%20to%20learn%20it.%20It%20stands%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20patience%20and%20skill%20that%20define%20this%20timeless%20Kashmiri%20tradition.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPreserving%20