smen%20like%20Khan%20are%20training%20budding%20artists%20who%20also%20receive%20stipends%20and%20allowances%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20further%20promote%20Jamawar%20patchwork%2C%20we%20are%20actively%20introducing%20it%20under%20various%20government%20schemes%20aimed%20at%20preserving%20and%20expanding%20this%20heritage%20craft.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20workshop%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20unusual%20to%20find%20young%20men%20and%20women%20sitting%20beside%20him%2C%20observing%2C%20asking%20questions%2C%20learning%20slowly%20%E2%80%94%20stitch%20by%20stitch.%20Some%20come%20from%20families%20of%20artisans%2C%20others%20are%20drawn%20by%20curiosity.%20What%20they%20all%20share%20is%20the%20desire%20to%20keep%20something%20alive%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20a%20technique%2C%20but%20a%20way%20of%20seeing%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20time%20when%20traditional%20crafts%20are%20often%20reduced%20to%20souvenirs%2C%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20story%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20quiet%20work%20being%20done%20across%20Kashmir%20%E2%80%94%20reminds%20us%20that%20these%20art%20forms%20still%20have%20life%2C%20meaning%2C%20and%20a%20future%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20people%20who%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Leila%20Badyari%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748265369000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D439194%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20a%20life-changing%20accident%20in%201998%2C%20Srinagar-based%20artisan%20Haji%20Ghulam%20Rasool%20Khan%20returned%20to%20the%20forgotten%20craft%20of%20Jamawar%20patchwork.%20From%20his%20home%20workshop%2C%20he%20not%20only%20mastered%20the%20art%20but%20brought%20it%20global%20acclaim%2C%20preserving%20a%20piece%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20soul%2C%20one%20intricate%20stitch%20at%20a%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Irfan%20Ami