%20The%20team%20has%20undertaken%20some%20transformational%20projects%20over%20the%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20Swachh%20Worli%20Koliwada%20project%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20team%20bend%20their%20heads%20over%20a%20scalable%20model%20that%20would%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366571%2Fkalpana-sankar-hand-in-hand-india-access-to-financial-inclusion-tamil-nadu-percy-barnevik%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreate%20livelihood%20opportunities%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20Kolis.%20Launched%20on%205%20June%202018%20(World%20Environment%20Day)%2C%20the%20project%20envisioned%20the%2065-acre%20Koliwada%20area%20as%20a%20self-sustaining%20zero-waste%20neighbourhood.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20all%20responsible%20for%20our%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parikh%20and%20team%20told%20the%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20proposed%20collection%20centres%20where%20the%20waste%20is%20segregated%20and%20organised%2C%20dry%20waste%20is%20recycled%2C%20and%20manure%20from%20the%20wet%20waste%20is%20used%20for%20kitchen%20gardens.%20We%20also%20got%20the%20contractors%20to%20train%20and%20appoint%20several%20community%20members%20for%20the%20project.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0The%20idea%20was%20to%20create%20a%20model%20that%20would%20have%20a%20sway%20over%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20waste%20disposition%20ideals.%20The%20project%20involved%20developing%20participatory%2C%20ground-up%20processes%20and%20systems%2C%20along%20with%20the%20community%2C%20BMC%20and%20experts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDEm4IIfNC1g%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDEm4IIfNC1g%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5