0heritage%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Bhendi%20Bazaar%20Gharana%2C%20where%20music%20lovers%20could%20access%20old%20recordings%2C%20archival%20data%20on%20the%20history%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Egharana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20paintings%20of%20Anjanibai%20Malpekar%20the%20well%20known%20disciple%20of%20the%20gharana%2C%20who%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20muses%20of%20Raja%20Ravi%20Varma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParikh%20elaborates%20on%20their%20mentorship%20programme%2C%20which%20enabled%20three%20children%20from%20Worli%20Koliwada%20who%20were%20already%20learning%20classical%20music%20to%20engage%20with%20some%20of%20the%20practising%20musicians%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Egharana%3C%2Fem%3E.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20then%20selected%20to%20be%20mentored%20by%20Shubha%20Joshi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20disciples%20of%20this%20%3Cem%3Egharana%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20project%20%E2%80%98Reclaiming%20Shakti%E2%80%99%20in%20partnership%20with%20Akshara%20Foundation%20focused%20on%20bolstering%20the%20safety%20measures%20in%20the%20Shakti%20Mill%20area%20following%20the%20gruesome%20gang%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20photojournalist%20here%20in%202013.%20Sadly%2C%20this%20project%20did%20not%20see%20the%20light%20of%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20G5A%20cityLAB%20worked%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20D%20Ward%20of%20the%20BMC%20to%20launch%20the%20Legacy%20plaque%20project%20(honouring%20almost%20100%20cultural%2C%20political%2C%20and%20social%20community%20members%20and%20institutions%20of%20Mumbai).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20are%20just%20a%20sliver%20of%20the%20projects%20that%20G5A%20has%20championed%2C%20there%20are%20several%20more%20in%20the%20works.%20Through%20each%20of%20its%20endeavours%20within%20the%20studio%20and%20beyond%2C%20G5A%20is%20adding%20a%20bold%20dynamic%20to%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20artistic%20skyline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Vidya%20Gowri%20Venkatesh%2C%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%20Anuradha%20Pa