on-success-stories%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etravels%20across%20India%20spawned%20a%20cycle%20of%20insights%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20world%20of%20sea%20turtles%2C%20lessons%20which%20hold%20in%20good%20stead%20even%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20when%20turtle%20researcher%20and%20conservationist%20Ed%20Moll%20came%20to%20India%20to%20conduct%20a%20freshwater%20turtle%20study%2C%20Bhaskar%20stepped%20in%20to%20help%20survey%20the%20highly%20endangered%20Northern%20river%20terrapin%20(%3Cem%3EBatagur%20baska%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20which%20nests%20on%20coastal%20beaches%20along%20with%20olive%20ridleys.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202010%2C%20during%20the%2030th%20Annual%20Symposium%20on%20Sea%20Turtle%20Biology%20and%20Conservation%20in%20Goa%2C%20the%20International%20Sea%20Turtle%20Society%20presented%20him%20with%20a%20Sea%20Turtle%20Champions%20Award%20for%20his%20outstanding%20contributions%20to%20sea%20turtle%20research%20through%20his%20surveys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhaskar%20passed%20away%20in%20March%202023%2C%20but%20left%20behind%20a%20legacy%20%E2%80%94%20his%20very%20own%20footprints%20in%20the%20sand%20%E2%80%94%20for%20generations%20of%20conservationists%20to%20follow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Vidya%20Gowri%20Venkatesh%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mongabay.com%2Fshort-article%2Fthe-turtle-walker-satish-bhaskar-sea-turtle-conservationist%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Turtle%20Walker%3A%20Satish%20Bhaskar%2C%20sea%20turtle%20conservationist%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20Rhett%20Ayers%20Butler%2C%20Published%20on%2028%20March%202025.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5